              <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Context-Rich Decisions</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                When someone needs to decide, all relevant context is automatically assembled. "Is this customer profitable?" answered with complete financial context in seconds.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 5 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 ease-out">
