            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Risk detection: Previously invisible patterns now surface automatically</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600">Decision consistency: Same situation, same outcome, every time</p>
